gin\": 1242, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.3894067773957963e-13, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Pistorius shot Steenkamp\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"a locked bathroom door\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"his home\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has maintained that he did not kill her in a fit of anger during a Valentine's Day argument, as prosecutors argued, and said instead he had mistaken her for an intruder.During the trial, which garnered global attention, Pistorius pleaded not guilty to one charge of murder and a firearms charge associated with Steenkamp's killing.Related NewsMany children still unvaccinated, Reps committee chair lamentsVandalism major threat to power supply - TCNFG unveils new education policies, focuses on implementationHe was initially convicted of manslaughter in 2014 and sentenced to five years.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fit\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"a Valentine's Day argument\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecutors\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"an intruder\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"the trial\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"global attention\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"one charge\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"murder\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"a firearms charge\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"Steenkamp's killing\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"Related NewsMany children\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"Reps committee chair lamentsVandalism major threat\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"power supply - TCNFG\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"new education policies\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"manslaughter\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a higher court overturned the conviction and upgraded it to murder a year later, increasing his sentence to six years in prison.The ruling was appealed by prosecutors who claimed the sentence was too lenient.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a higher court\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"the conviction\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"his sentence\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"six years\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"The ruling\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecutors\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"the sentence\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius' sentence was increased to 13 years and five months by South Africa's Supreme Court of Appeal in 2017.Pistorius became eligible for parole in March 2023, due to a law for inmates who have served half of their sentence and met conditions such as good behavior.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2078, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\",